pullRequest.body:
We deprecate  `alephIdx.initialSeg`, `alephIdx`, `alephIdx.relIso`, `Aleph'.relIso`, and `aleph'Equiv`, which were just stating this idea in slightly different ways.

We also make `Cardinal.aleph` an order embedding.
